    "In all the main experiments, we fine-tune the Llama-3-8b-Instruct models (Unsloth) using QLoRA with adapter ranks set to 16.",
    "We note that across all faithfulness experiments foot_0, we compute CoT Pred Match -the fraction of data points for which the final answer obtained by prompting the LLM with a perturbed CoT is the same as the answer obtained by prompting the LLM with the original CoT.",
    "In the case of Early Termination and Filler Substitution tests, higher values of CoT Pred Match generally indicate that a greater number of points are likely to have CoT reasonings that are not faithful.",
